channel.title: Weird dream
channel.description: Ok, i guess this is a weird post, but its something i have been searching for for awhile, and i cannot find any thing about what it might mean. Both me and a couple people i know have had similar dreams, which i find very odd... Ok, in general the dream is just normal, but then we end up fighting/beating some one up, well we go to swing at them, and our arm moves really really slow, and we just can't seem to hit them hard at all. We have had a few dreams like this, so i guess i have two questions, has any one else had this happen? and does any one know what it may mean?
